owltools.gaf.io

Class OpenAnnotationRDFWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • owltools.gaf.io.OpenAnnotationRDFWriter

  • public class OpenAnnotationRDFWriter
extends Object
    Generates and writes RDF Models conforming to http://www.openannotation.org/spec/core/core.html from GeneAnnotation objects. TODOs: - use subProperties of hasBody and hasTarget? - use subClass of oa:Annotation - use own vocabulary for evidence - fix evidence - decide on policy for isoforms - vocabulary for GPAD relation - decide on model for annotation extensions - add all GPAD fields - include option to have labels and other data from bioentities (tho expected to come from elsewhere) - decide on URI policy for bioentities, entities in WITH column - many more things...
    Author:
    cjm
